perfcenter.baseclass

Class Queue

  • java.lang.Object
    • perfcenter.baseclass.Queue
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    QueueSim

    public class Queue
extends java.lang.Object
    Queue class is the primitive queue which resides in all the components of distributed system. This class has all the parameters and performance metrics of the queue, which can be set by the method solving it. It also has information about where it belongs in the system.
